Steinmeier Wants Greek Debt Restructuring as Option, Bild Says

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-05-15T11:58:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/steinmeier-wants-greek-debt-restructuring-as-option-bild-says.html
A restructuring of  Greece ’s debt
musn’t be “excluded” if the current adjustment measures don’t
work,  Bild am Sonntag  reported, citing German opposition leader
Frank-Walter Steinmeier.  Private investors should also bear the cost of the
financial crisis, Bild cited Steinmeier as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
